{"tid":1753383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當選咗嘅區議員肯行多一步 政府即刻冇棋","createTime":"2019-11-25T02:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T22:42:38.000Z","uid":265545,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7676a16d6b2605c2145eb8c0a23541a96edd0c35","tid":1753383,"uid":265545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"依家18區贏曬, 民主派議員可以立即組織一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">執政聯盟</span></strong></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n只要林鄭唔回應五大訴求， 以後政府行任何政策， 區選執政聯盟都要反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單睇尋日幾十個外國議員嚟香港監察投票過程， 我哋已經知道香港進入咗一個<ins>大國共管</ins>嘅狀態， 一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由人民選出嚟嘅區選執政聯盟有足夠嘅bargaining power同外國傳媒嘅吸引力</span>， 如果每次政府政策都同盟選嘅執政聯盟意見相反，我可以預示到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成個政府唔會運作到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 因為政府唔似區選執政聯盟一樣有民意授權<br />\n<br />\n同時 區選執政聯盟可以利用每個月18區幾千萬嘅人工開支，去做政策研究同政策倡議， <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em><ins>成立影子政府</ins></em></strong></span></span> 到時政府只有兩條路揀一係一國一制，取消選舉 二係直選行政長官,增加自己認受性"},{"pid":"3ef81532ab82c43a3f1499168f4c56fd34120498","tid":1753383,"uid":116572,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7676a16d6b2605c2145eb8c0a23541a96edd0c35","tid":1753383,"uid":265545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"依家18區贏曬, 民主派議員可以立即組織一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">